# Nothing rendered or regenerable is version-controlled. The MP4 is published
# as a GitHub Release asset, not committed — it's 3.4 MB of binary that bloats
# every clone and can't be learned from. The source files (.html/.md/.py) ARE
# committed as the reference build; everything ignored below is reproduced via
# voiceover.py + the ffmpeg recipes in workflows/phase-5-audio.md and
# example/README.md § "Reproducing the render".
*.mp3
out/final.mp4

# Transcript is regenerated by `npx hyperframes transcribe` / Whisper
transcript.json
voiceover.srt
voiceover.txt
voiceover.tsv
voiceover.vtt
